description:
Aims and Objectives:
1.	To promote awareness of the financial services industry and encourage interest in this career pathway amongst young women;

2.	To empower young women interested in pursuing a career in investment banking and corporate finance through industry-specific education and unique platforms for discussion;

3.	To provide young women with the opportunity to interact with female role models in the industry through exchanging ideas and experiences;

4.	To encourage leadership, initiative and intellectual conversation amongst young female talents through building and strengthening a toolkit of skills suited to working in the financial services industry; and

5.	To distinguish and highlight female presence in the corporate finance industry through fostering a supportive and motivating environment for learning.

